name: Lean Beef Patty - Textual Inversion
description:
This ti was somewhat of a challenge, a friend of mine told me I couldn't do a ti of a female bodybuilder look good. I disagree and here are the results.

Lean Beef Patty, leanbeefpatty on instagram, is an instagram model and fitness advocate with over 4.6 million followers.

This was quite the fun challenge (not challenging tho) to do and I hope that there a a few people on here that find enjoyment with this TI.

Still learning and improving the progress of the training, any feedback is welcome.

Feel free to leave me a tip/buy me a coffee if you like what I am doing :)
